title: 12 More Books - November 2015 (gnv64)
description:
Another collection of ebooks for this month, 10 in ePUB & 2 in PDF format.
Covers included in a separate folder:

01. 4 Weeks to Healthy Digestion - Norton Greenberger
02. A Couple's Guide to Sexual Addi - Paldrom Collins
03. Becoming Bulletproof: An Uncommon Approach to Building a Resilient Body - Tim Anderson
04. Bloodline of the Gods - Nick Redfern
05. From 0 to Infinity in 26 Centuries: The Extraordinary Story of Maths - Chris Waring
06. Hacking: An unofficial anonymous guide - Windows and Internet - Jonathan Jones
07. How to Hack - The Ultimate Hacking Book- Kevin Smith
08. Secret Model Beauty - Lindsey Lockwood
09. The New York Times Book of Math - Gina Kolata
10. The Petite Advantage Diet - Jim Karas
11. Training for Both Ends of the Leash - Kate Perry
12. Weights on the Ball Workbook - Step-by-Step Guide with Over 350 Photos - Steve Stiefel
